@NODE "REQUESTERS" "Requestery"

  - Print
      - nastavenè hranic pro tisk - buá v mm nebo jejich nakreslenèm
        (stisknéte tlaûètko myÆi a vytvoØte hraniûnè obdælnèk)
      - nastavenè bitovæ hloubky tisku (od ÐB po 256 barev)
      - potlaûenè vyjèÖdénè listu z tiskêrny
      - nastavenè tisku rêmeûku okolo obrêzku

  - Save ILBM
      - nastavenè rozmérò a bitovæ hloubky obrêzku
      - pØepènaû strip znamenê, Öe obrêzek bude rozdélen na 9 ûêstè,
        aby bylo moÖnæ zobrazit i velmi velkæ obrêzky (uloÖen bude
        samozØejmé vcelku)

  - Change @{"Settings..." LINK "PREFERENCES"}
      - nastavenè vlastnè nebo sdèlenæ obrazovky
      - zména nêzvu sdèlenæ obrazovky
      - zména zobrazovacèho müdu a bitovæ hloubky
      - nastavenè zêkladnèch pèsem (serif, sans serif, deco, typewriter,
        script)

  - Substitute FONT
      - nêhrada neexistujècèho pèsma buá nékterìm ze zêkladnèch pèsem
        nebo pØèmou volbou z requesteru. PØi volbé "INCLUDE" se pouÖijè
        zêkladnè pèsma, pomocè "USE" dojde k otevØenè requesteru

@ENDNODE


@NODE "BATCH" "Dêvkovê konverze"

  Pokud si pØejete provæst dêvkovou konverzi, pouÖijte standardnè skript
 shellu "s:spat", kterì je dodêvanì s WB. Zde je jak na to:

  1. Spusåte CLI.
  2. NapiÆte nêsledujècè pØèkaz (celì najednou):

     "s:spat <cesta k MetaView>/MetaView <zdrojovê cesta>/<Æablona>
     <cèlovê cesta>/ SAVE <@{"formêt vìstupu" LINK "FORMATE"}>"


   <cesta k MetaView> - cesta k programu MetaView
   <zdrojovê cesta>   - cesta ke zdrojovìm datòm
   <Æablona>          - Æablona pro volbu souborò
   <cèlovê cesta>     - cesta k cèlovìm datòm (musè existovat)
   <formêt vìstupu>   - formêt dat, kterì si pØejete


 PØèklad: "s:spat work:MetaView/MetaView cd0:clips/#?.wmf Cliparts: SAVE DR2D"

@ENDNODE



@NODE "PREFERENCES" "Nastavenè"

  - nastavenè je uloÖeno v ENV: a ENVARC:, v proménnæ MetaView.prefs
  - jednê se o soubor v ASCII, kterì lze jednoduÆe editovat


    Zêkladnè nastavenè:

      SCREENMODE=$8004
      SCREENWIDTH=-1
      SCREENHEIGHT=-1
      SCREENDEPTH=4
      CUSTOMSCREEN=TRUE
      PUBLICSCREEN=Workbench
      SERIF_FONT=Times.font
      SANS_FONT=Helvetica.font
      TYPE_FONT=Courier.font
      SCRIPT_FONT=Times.font
      DECO_FONT=Times.font
      PRINT_DEVICE=printer.device
      PRINT_UNIT=0
      PROGRESS=0  -> 0 - nic; 1 - pouze V/V operace; 2 - V/V a pØekreslovênè

@ENDNODE


@NODE "FORMATE" "Formêty"

Formêt    Popis

@{I}Vstupnè:@{UI}

  AMF     @{B}A@{UB}miga @{B}M@{UB}eta@{B}F@{UB}ile
          mòj vlastnè formêt, nezêvislì na zaØèzenè, rychlì a
          zaloÖenì na AmigaMetaFormat.library

  WMF     @{B}W@{UB}indows @{B}M@{UB}eta@{B}F@{UB}ile
          na PC (mnoho CD s cliparty)

  CLP     @{B}Cl@{UB}i@{B}p@{UB}board
          formêt schrênky na PC (Windows)

  WPG     @{B}W@{UB}ord@{B}p@{UB}erfect @{B}G@{UB}raphic
          na PC (WordPerfect), nékterê CD s cliparty

  CDR     @{B}C@{UB}orel @{B}Dr@{UB}awing
          na PC a takæ na Macintoshi (CorelDraw),
          ale bohuÖel chybè popis formêtu

  DR2D    @{B}Dr@{UB}awing @{B}2D@{UB}
          na Amize (PageStream, DrawStudio, ProVector atd.)

  DXF     @{B}D@{UB}rawing E@{B}x@{UB}change @{B}F@{UB}ile
          na PC a UNIXu (AutoCAD), (CADovskæ soubory)

  FIG     na Amize (AmiFIG nebo XFig) a UNIXu (XFig)

  DSDR    @{B}D@{UB}raw@{B}S@{UB}tudio @{B}Dr@{UB}awing
          na Amize (DrawStudio)

  CGM     @{B}C@{UB}omputer@{B}G@{UB}raphic@{B}M@{UB}etafile
          na Amize (WordWorth, i barvy), PC nebo UNIXu

  GEM     na Amize (WordWorth, bez barev), PC nebo Atari


@{I}Vìstupnè:@{UI}

  AMF     @{B}A@{UB}miga @{B}M@{UB}eta@{B}F@{UB}ile
          mòj vlastnè formêt, nezêvislì na zaØèzenè, rychlì a
          zaloÖenì na AmigaMetaFormat.library

  CGM     @{B}C@{UB}omputer@{B}G@{UB}raphic@{B}M@{UB}etafile
          na Amize (WordWorth, i barvy), PC nebo UNIXu

  GEM     na Amize (WordWorth, bez barev), PC nebo Atari

  EPS     @{B}E@{UB}ncapsulated @{B}P@{UB}ost@{B}S@{UB}cript
          na vÆech platformêch, lze takæ tisknout na PS tiskêrnêch

  HPGL    @{B}H@{UB}ewlett-@{B}P@{UB}ackard @{B}G@{UB}raphics @{B}L@{UB}anguage
          pouÖitè u plotrò

  DR2D    @{B}Dr@{UB}awing @{B}2D@{UB}
          na Amize (PageStream, DrawStudio, ProVector atd.)

  ILBM    @{B}I@{UB}nter@{B}l@{UB}eaved @{B}B@{UB}it@{B}M@{UB}ap
          na Amize (DPaint atd.), bitmapovì formêt

  AI      @{B}A@{UB}dobe @{B}I@{UB}llustrator

  WMF     @{B}W@{UB}indows @{B}M@{UB}eta@{B}F@{UB}ile
          na PC (mnoho CD s cliparty)

  JMF     @{B}J@{UB}ava @{B}M@{UB}eta@{B}F@{UB}ile
          pouÖitè na WWW, dalÆè informace na mæ strênce


@ENDNODE


@NODE "HISTORY" "Historie"

  @{"HISTORY" LINK "MetaView.history/MAIN"}

  * Ponechêno v originêle *

  Version 2.3
    NEW
      - enhanced DXF Import
      - Export WMF
      - Export JMF
      - changeable printer.device and unit
      - change automatical the filename extension
      - Import DSDR
      - Import CGM
  Version 2.2
    NEW
      - Import GEM, Export AI, prepared for WMF and JMF
      - ILBM-export and print are made with stripes for creating pictures
        larger than free chipmem (Geoffrey A. Gass, you want this)
      - zoom function (now you can better read your DXF-files :-)
  Version 2.1
    NEW and FIXED:
      - there was a bug in ILBM-export created in Version 2.0, now fixed
        (thanks to Jon Peterson)
      - include Version in Screentitle and Aboutwindow (also ARexxPort)
        (thanks to jon Peterson)
      - include ARexx-Examples
      - include 'tabs.gadget' and 'SetPatch' (ˋ Amiga Technologie)
      - ignore comments on start of DXF files
      - faster DXF parsing if $EXTMIN/MAX present
      - WPG files with colors and switch top/down
        (thanks to Andreas Kleinert for WPG-example)
      - no exit if tabs.gadget not found
    CHANGES in 'amigametaformat.library'
      - complete dr2d.driver and hpgl.driver
  Version 2.0
    NEW:
      - change from pd to shareware
      - support Screenmode and PublicScreens
      - support transparent
      - many new Importformats
      - HPGL- and DR2D-export
    FIXED:
      - fixed bug in ILBM-export when width not a multiple from 16
        (thanx to MagicBox Inc.)
      - the long terrible bug, i hope, was not my fault, but an error on
        'mathieeesingbas.library' from Kick 3.1
      - fixed bug in ILBM-export for Kick 2.0
  Version 1.4
    NEW:
      - preserve picture-aspect
        thanks to Geoffrey A. Gass
      - enhanced ILBM-export
      - enhanced printing, also from CLI
    FIXED:
      - Installer-Bug,
        thanks to Geoffrey A. Gass
    CHANGES in 'amigametaformat.library'
      - please look at 'amigametaformat.readme'
  Version 1.3
    NEW:
      - CLI-Arguments
      - batchmode to convert many Cliparts (with s:dpat)
      - automatic gfxtype recognite
    FIXED:
      - Bug with ASL-Requester (mixing file- and pathname),
        thanks to Andreas Kleinert
      - No more 'unexpect End of File' if loading correct WMF,
        thanks to Harry W. Turner II and Geoffrey A. Gass
      - Better colors in WMF-files
    CHANGES in 'amigametaformat.library'
      - please look at 'amigametaformat.readme'
  Version 1.2
    Second public release, first within the AMF-Library.lha.
    NEW:
      - WMF-import
    CHANGES in 'amigametaformat.libary'
      - fix some bugs in CGM-driver with AMF_POLYGON and AMF_FILL_POLY

@ENDNODE


